程序包 Model

类 SessionContext

java.lang.Object
Model.SessionContext
public class SessionContext extends Object
Represents the context of a user session in the Smart Finance Application. This class encapsulates the current intent, filled slots, missing slots, and confirmation status for managing conversational interactions, such as intent recognition and slot-filling processes.
版本:
1.0
作者:
Group 19
